on the door, no answer.

25
00:04:15,055 --> 00:04:17,223
So, he's hoping that
you'll pass by,

26
00:04:17,224 --> 00:04:18,958
make sure that Delia's okay.

27
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,526
And why can't you do it?

28
00:04:20,527 --> 00:04:22,795
Because my shift ended while you
were eating your breakfast.

29
00:04:22,796 --> 00:04:24,896
Oh, right.

30
00:04:25,598 --> 00:04:26,966
Let me take care of that for you.

31
00:04:26,967 --> 00:04:29,467
Oh, thanks. Yeah, just top it up?

32
00:04:30,103 --> 00:04:31,871
- The cell phone.
- Oh.

33
00:04:31,872 --> 00:04:34,440
No, it's fine.

34
00:04:34,441 --> 00:04:37,342
It's been sitting in that
box for three months.

35
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:41,648
- It's comfortable there.
- Uh-huh.

36
00:04:41,649 --> 00:04:45,018
- Get some sleep.
- Oh, will you stop by Ernie's on the way?

37
00:04:45,019 --> 00:04:47,120
There was a call about some
sort of fracas over there.

38
00:04:47,121 --> 00:04:51,491
- A "frah-cas"?
