42
00:05:35,768 --> 00:05:39,637
Delia, it's Hazel.
I'm letting myself in.

43
00:05:41,641 --> 00:05:43,408
Delia?

44
00:06:28,588 --> 00:06:31,858
Yeah, I'm at Delia's. Get
over here as fast as you can,

45
00:06:31,859 --> 00:06:34,959
and call Spere. Yeah.

46
00:07:48,935 --> 00:07:51,269
You got here fast.

47
00:07:51,637 --> 00:07:53,472
This is wild.

48
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:55,440
Yeah.

49
00:07:56,809 --> 00:07:58,244
You knew her?

50
00:07:58,245 --> 00:08:01,147
Yeah. All my life.

51
00:08:01,148 --> 00:08:03,247
She went to my mom's church.

52
00:08:04,317 --> 00:08:07,318
I've never seen anything like this.

53
00:08:08,955 --> 00:08:10,990
What can you tell?

54
00:08:10,991 --> 00:08:13,558
Well, it looks like a
knife to the neck.

55
00:08:13,559 --> 00:08:14,727
Yeah.

56
00:08:14,728 --> 00:08:16,629
But I'll have to bring
her to the city

57
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,865
