91
00:10:21,387 --> 00:10:23,189
Oh, God.

92
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:25,758
I'll... I'll get this.
I'll take him in the back.

93
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,625
Oh, thanks.

94
00:10:36,869 --> 00:10:40,673
I've been trying for months
to get her into hospice care.

95
00:10:40,674 --> 00:10:43,142
I knew this day was coming

96
00:10:43,143 --> 00:10:46,779
