was going to be like this.

97
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:50,616
So, did she have any
family heirlooms

98
00:10:50,617 --> 00:10:53,386
or expensive jewelry or
anything in the house?

99
00:10:53,387 --> 00:10:55,321
You think someone was
trying to rob her?

100
00:10:55,322 --> 00:10:57,123
I don't know.

101
00:10:57,124 --> 00:11:00,892
Was she expecting anyone,
I mean, besides you?

102
00:11:01,394 --> 00:11:03,427
No.

103
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:09,835
Can I see her?

104
00:11:09,836 --> 00:11:12,470
Not... Not yet. Let's...

105
00:11:12,705 --> 00:11:14,705
In a bit.

106
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:26,952
