this time of the morning,

225
00:18:54,667 --> 00:18:57,234
but you don't look like a trucker.

226
00:18:58,203 --> 00:19:00,170
I'm not.

227
00:19:03,842 --> 00:19:07,412
Well, cook should be here any
minute if you want to see a menu.

228
00:19:07,413 --> 00:19:10,848
Just berries, if you have.

229
00:19:11,216 --> 00:19:13,250
Yeah.

230
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:32,036
Sorry, it comes with melon.

231
00:19:36,508 --> 00:19:38,442
(CHUCKLES)

232
00:19:43,148 --> 00:19:45,115
Are you a doctor?

233
00:19:49,221 --> 00:19:52,624
I specialize

234
00:19:52,625 --> 00:19:58,128
in methods that conventional
medicine ignores.

235
00:20:00,265 --> 00:20:02,666
