236
00:20:03,769 --> 00:20:07,206
Many diseases can manifest
through our environment.

237
00:20:07,207 --> 00:20:10,309
What we eat, how we live,

238
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:13,610
and just as we may
create our illness,

239
00:20:14,046 --> 00:20:16,513
our bodies can be healed.

240
00:20:18,884 --> 00:20:23,020
And that works on, uh...

241
00:20:25,724 --> 00:20:27,926
