250
00:20:57,189 --> 00:21:02,127
And straightway the
damsel arose and walked,

251
00:21:02,128 --> 00:21:04,661
for she was of the age of 12.

252
00:21:05,831 --> 00:21:09,199
And they were overcome with wonder.

253
00:21:15,007 --> 00:21:18,275
Mark 5:42.

